        "testimonial_nTNgPK": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/laboderma_-_2026-02-18T223145.715.png",
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Jessica R.",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<p>I drink coffee every day, and honestly my teeth had really yellowed over time. I tried these strips a little skeptical... and I was blown away. You can really see the difference, even after just a few uses.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_ETkTzi": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/laboderma_-_2026-02-18T222539.933.png",
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Ashley M.",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<p>I was really self-conscious about my smile. I always smiled while hiding my teeth. Since I started using these strips, I feel so much more comfortable. It sounds silly, but it really changes your confidence.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_zTVfEw": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/laboderma_-_2026-02-18T222700.807.png",
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Brittany V.",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<p>I used them on my commute before a date 😅 Super convenient, they stay in place and they're so easy to apply. And most importantly, you can actually see the results. Totally worth it.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_7HyWHm": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/laboderma_-_2026-02-18T223308.606.png",
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Brandon T.",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<p>Before buying, I showed the ingredients to my dentist. He confirmed everything was safe and non-abrasive. That put my mind at ease. And after trying them, I can say they really do work.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_6pwnWz": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/laboderma_-_2026-02-18T222944.011.png",
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Tyler L.",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<p>I've been smoking for years, so my teeth weren't the whitest... I thought it was a lost cause. These strips really surprised me. The change is visible, even for me.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_Tt6haV": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
