            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Jason P.",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<p>I've tried charcoal, multiple whitening toothpastes, other brands... with no real results. With these, from the very first use, I saw a real difference. I was convinced right away.</p>"
